title: Taricheiai/Zouchis
description: An ancient settlement located at the eastern end of the Zouchis Limne (modern Bahiret el Bibane on the Tunisian coast). The modern name of the site is Henchir el-Mdeina.

properties.description: Location determined by eye in Google Earth using description and Figure 65 in Slim 2004. Dates after BAtlas.
